# - Try to find CFITSIO
# Once done this will define
#
#  CFITSIO_FOUND - system has CFITSIO
#  CFITSIO_INCLUDE_DIR - the CFITSIO include directory
#  CFITSIO_LIBRARIES - Link these to use CFITSIO

